'''Suicide Tuesday''' (or '''Tuesday blues''', '''Ecstasy Tuesday''') is a slang term for the depressive period following the use of [[Ecstasy (drug)|Ecstasy]].
This term is currently thought to be in use in Australia, South Africa and England.

Suicide Tuesday refers to the tuesday after ecstacy use generally on the weekend proceeding it, either on the friday or saturday night, and usually following the monday at work (or school) the user has the tendency to become somewhat depressed on the tuesday.
There is no real empirical evidence for this occurence, it is largely just a talked about occurence. 

It is similar in concept to [[Mondayitis]]

Similarly, "Suicide Tuesday" is the phrase used to describe the depression following a weekend of heavy [[Methamphetamine|Crystal Meth]] usage. 

